menu "HardFOC Vortex HAL"

    config HARDFOC_HAL_CANOPENNODE_SLAVE
        bool "Build CANopenNode slave stack (upstream + blank CO driver)"
        default n
        help
            Compiles CANopenNode into the hf-hal-vortex-v1 component via hf-core CMake.
            Vendor tree: third_party/CANopenNode (git submodule).

            After enabling, initialize the submodule from the HAL repo root:

                git submodule update --init --recursive third_party/CANopenNode

            With the blank driver, CiA logic runs but no frames are sent on TWAI.
            Replace CO_driver with a BaseCan/TWAI-backed port for a live bus (single RX owner).

endmenu
